{"tid":2345860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都覺得柳俊江撞26單野勁有可疑","createTime":"2020-12-30T01:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T13:16:46.000Z","uid":261505,"like":9,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"05c382c231deb2e04061b288dd0d739ffe432842","tid":2345860,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:03:16.000Z","msg":"個電單車司機似中共派黎 想屈721比人打到豬頭咁既柳爺<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aekHCjV1UGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaekHCjV1UGg&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGfZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=35199201\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aekHCjV1UGg</a><br />\n<br />\n個26車手咁樣衝出去似係有target<br />\n有無連登探員幫手查下？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>尖沙嘴晚上發生一宗交通意外，一名司機涉嫌危險駕駛被捕，據知被捕司機為39歲前TVB主播柳俊江。事發於晚上7時許，一輛私家車沿漆咸道南往九龍方向行駛，至沿梳士巴利道與漆咸道南交界時，私家車懷疑未有依交通燈號指示停車，與駛至的電單車發生相撞。<br />\n<br />\n鐵騎士手及腳受傷，清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，警方經調查後發現私家車司機的酒精測試有度數，但沒有超標，以涉嫌危險駕駛被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n據知，被捕的私家車司機為前TVB主播柳俊江，《蘋果》事後曾多次致電給他，但每次均接通後立即cut線。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f6398d992d6b59a17ee3ea50f0f09b9741325d3","tid":2345860,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e019bafd3bc4a3dd6cefd75bf9c6cf159344ce3","tid":2345860,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"你一係冇車牌<br />\n一係考完個牌冇揸過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05314d4d98